languages.text: "Среди тех красных жрецов были выжившие — хорошо. Они разнесут весть о том, что перечащим воле Домин уготована смерть".

languages.text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: «Hubo supervivientes entre esos sacerdotes rojos... Me alegro. Correrá la voz de que la muerte persigue a quienes desafían la voluntad de{mf|l| la} Domin».
languages.original_text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: 「あの赤の法師の中にも生存者がいました…それは良かった。彼らはドミンの意思に逆らう者には死が訪れるという噂を広めることでしょう」
languages.original_text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: “那些红袍神甫之中还有幸存者，这很好。他们会散播消息，让所有人知道，那些胆敢忤逆秘者的人注定难逃一死。”
languages.original_text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: "Es gab Überlebende unter diesen roten Priestern ... gut. Sie werden allen erzählen, dass der Tod all jene holt, die sich dem Willen {mf|des|der} Domin widersetzen.
languages.original_text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: « Tous les prêtres rouges ne sont pas mort. Excellent. Ils feront savoir que la mort frappera quiconque s'opposera à la volonté {mf|du|de la} Domin. »
languages.original_text: "There were survivors among those red priests — good. They will spread the word that death will come to those who defy the Domin's will."

languages.text: "Kızıl rahiplerden sağ kalanlar olmuş. Güzel. Domin'in iradesine karşı çıkanları ölümün beklediğini herkese duyururlar."
